<h2 class="wikiHeadline2" id="H-RichFaces332"><a href="/2009/07/08/rich-faces-face-2-face-meeting-review#H-RichFaces332">RichFaces 3.3.2</a></h2>
<p class="wikiPara">
The 3.3.2 release is going to be a performance &amp; bug fix release.  We are planning on releasing the CR1 in late August and the GA sometime in September.  Some of the highlights are:
</p>

<ul class="wikiUnorderedList">
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Remove internal CSS classes for performance optimizations <a href="https://jira.jboss.org/jira/browse/RF-7215" target="" class="regularLink">RF-7215</a>
</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Optimize JavaScipt initialization <a href="https://jira.jboss.org/jira/browse/RF-7215" target="" class="regularLink">RF-7246</a>
</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Example impovements <a href="https://jira.jboss.org/jira/secure/IssueNavigator.jspa?reset=true&amp;&amp;fixfor=12313512&amp;pid=12310341&amp;component=12312448&amp;sorter/field=resolution&amp;sorter/order=ASC&amp;sorter/field=status&amp;sorter/order=ASC&amp;sorter/field=priority&amp;sorter/order=DESC" target="" class="regularLink">Jiras</a>
</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Many others <a href="https://jira.jboss.org/jira/browse/RF/fixforversion/12313512" target="" class="regularLink">3.3.2.CR1 Jiras</a>
</li>
</ul>

<p class="wikiPara">
The 3.3.X branch will go into maintenance mode and will only have releases to cover critical issues, or if there are enough community contributions to warrant a release.  This will allow the team to focus on the 4.0 release.
</p>


<h2 class="wikiHeadline2" id="H-RichFaces400"><a href="/2009/07/08/rich-faces-face-2-face-meeting-review#H-RichFaces400">RichFaces 4.0.0</a></h2>
<div style="float:right;margin-left:20px;margin-bottom:20px;">
 <a href="/service/File/11982" target="" class="regularLink"><img src="/images/11982.jpeg"></a>
 <br>
